27 and it feels GOOD 🌞

TODAY IS THE DAY ••• #FRSAupcycled is finally out 🏹⏳🎞️

I had this project in my head for over a year and today it’s real. It’s out. I have been working on every detail for so long… After many failures, trial, and error, and mainly the fact of not selling out from collections & being stuck with all those clothes made me realize I needed to do something different if I wanted to be part of the fashion industry.

The process of upcycling clothing felt just right for me. Not only you are helping with the overconsumption, waste, pollution, and environmental crisis, but it’s also just so fucking cool to give these authentic and GOOD QUALITY pieces a second, third, or fourth home. Like fine wine, they just get better with time.

I’m proud to say that this collection is fully eco-friendly, made out of second-hand garments that hold such a special place in my heart. I went to so many thrift stores around the U.S. collecting each piece, to the final result which is what you get today. By supporting this project, you’re not only supporting a hard-working 27-year-old woman, but you’re also making a difference in this world. You are contributing to a more sustainable future and prioritizing what really matters. Thank you so much and as always, I hope you love it as much as I do.🕊
